                valid_operations.append(f'{current_result}*{num}= {new_current_result}')
                valid_operations.append(f'{current_result}/{num}= {new_current_result}')

    return f"SOLUTION: YES\nOPERATIONS: {' -> '.join(ops_list)}\nRESULT: {target}"
